YOKO's rebuttal to "not make him look like a
villain." so we all, including myself, worked
down to the wire to adjust the balance for
that aspect.</p>
<p class="para"><b>Saito:</b> In the game, A2 usually ends up in the
villain spot, no matter what you do. She
didn't get much of a deep dive before, so
having her drawn out so carefully in the
anime must have been a salvation for all A2
fans.</p>
<p class="para"><b>Fujii:</b> When I was listening to 'POD'S
Podcast." I noticed there were a lot of
people who became A2 fans through the
anime. Including Chapter.6 and Chapter.17,
where we drew the episodes of her past as
Number 2. The understanding of A2's
character increased, resulting in the A2 you
